(46, 'choose_reason.element', '{\"title\":\"Trusted Platform\",\"description\":\"Welcome to our trusted platform where we bring you unbiased and reliable reviews of teachers and institutions. \\n\\nWe understand the importance of finding credible guidance for your educational journey, and our platform is committed to providing transparent insights. With thorough research and genuine user feedback, we ensure that you can make informed decisions in selecting the best educators and institutes for your preparation. \\n\\nTrust us to be your go-to destination for honest reviews, as we prioritise your success and satisfaction above all else.\",\"icon\":\"<i class=\\\"fas fa-handshake fa-3x\\\"><\\/i>\"}', '2022-02-13 09:57:25', '2023-07-17 14:48:16'),
(48, 'choose_reason.element', '{\"title\":\"Loyalty and Rewards\",\"description\":\"At our platform, we value your loyalty and dedication towards achieving your goals. As a token of our appreciation, we offer exclusive rewards and benefits for our loyal users. Earn points for every review you provide and for engaging with our community. These points can be redeemed for exciting rewards, including discounts on courses, personalised study plans, and much more. Your commitment to excellence deserves to be recognised, and we are delighted to offer these loyalty rewards as a small gesture of our gratitude.\",\"icon\":\"<i class=\\\"far fa-gem fa-3x\\\"><\\/i>\"}', '2022-02-13 09:59:35', '2023-07-27 14:03:43'),
(49, 'choose_reason.element', '{\"title\":\"Reviews and Ratings\",\"description\":\"Unlock the power of real-time reviews and ratings on our platform. Hear from fellow learners and experienced candidates who have firsthand knowledge of various teachers and institutions. Browse through detailed feedback, star ratings, and insightful comments to find the perfect match for your study needs. Our robust review system ensures that you get an authentic glimpse of the teaching quality, course content, and overall experience offered by each educator and institute. Trust the collective wisdom of our community to make the right choice.\",\"icon\":\"<i class=\\\"las la-star fa-3x\\\"><\\/i>\"}', '2022-02-13 10:00:03', '2023-07-17 14:50:49'),
